No,55/4/CF-67
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
(Department of Cabinet Affairs)
IMMEDIATE
New Delhi, the 2nd June, 1967.
The undersigned is directed to say that the President
has been pleased to direct that Dr. (Shrimati) Sarojini
Mahishi, Deputy Minister shall be attached to the Prime
Minister and shall perform such functions as may be
assigned to her by the Prime Minister from time to time.
(D.P. Chopra)
for Cabinet Secretary.
To.
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the Prime Minister/
tha, Joint Secretary to the Prime Minister/the Private
Secretary to the Prime Minister, for information.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the President/the
Secretary to the Vice-President, for information.
(D.P. Chopra)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
Copy forwarded to all Secretaries/Special Secretaries/
Additional Secretaries to the Government of India/Chairman,
Railway Board, for information.
Copy forwarded to al1 Ministries of the Government of
India/Lok Sabha Secretariat/Rajya Sabha Secretariat, for
information.
(D.P. Chopra)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
SS/250 Copies.
